title: Mas Nescafe DVD year 4 (Electronic Dance Music Videos) Ipod Read
description:
A Mexican corporation called Mas Nescafe or know world realeases periodic best hits of dance. Along with the music album came a DVD. Which i then ofcourse ripped. Yet enjoy this delightful ipod ready video.
I have only tested this on ipod touch and its stutter free.
I think ipod 5.5 will stutter for a specific reason or not play it can someone confirm.

Handbrake 0.9.1 macintosh

Settings custom ipod settings. Ipod setting:
Level: Cant Remember
Average kbps is 1500 kbps with 160 acc audio.
2 frame references with mixed references
subme 7 for best compression per bit and least visual artifacts
The buffer was set to 2500kbps but I do not see it spike that high.
640x480 aspect ratio. 
Deinterlace- Slow
Chapter Markers activated.
